  "texts": [
    "[27] In this way, no users in the network are required to trust any other user.",
    "This fundamental aspect of blockchain is responsible for already realized and potential advancements with LLMs concerning areas such as RAG, the training process, and even supply chain issues.",
    "Layer 2 Technologies.",
    "Apart from the fundamental components found within all blockchains, several external architectures interface with blockchains and further enhance their applicability.",
    "Typically, these external architectures are referred to as layer 2 technologies, as they sit a 'layer' above the 'layer 1' blockchain."
  ]
}